{"tid":761374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：野豬家族殺入獅子山","createTime":"2018-07-30T10:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T11:25:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea3ded7f3d4e6c902d80669d9a98481b247fdde","tid":761374,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:42:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180730/20464096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F20464096&d=FN1IPIf6A5MM2oCOz3XkkwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9866dce2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F20464096&h=f2cf858c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180730/20464096</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月30日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：野豬家族殺入獅子山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180730/large/a1203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180730%2Flarge%2Fa1203a.gif&h=ac90f992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■吳小姐在紅梅谷自然教育徑分別見到兩群近10隻野豬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n野豬芳蹤處處，《蘋果》噚日報道本來是馬騮盤踞嘅金山郊野公園，現時已經俾野豬群霸佔，估計因有人餵飼野豬有關。吳小姐本月21號同朋友行山都見到野豬，佢哋嗰日由黃大仙沙田坳道起步，經獅子山郊野公園諗住行去沙田。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180730/large/a1203b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180730%2Flarge%2Fa1203b.gif&h=221ffe71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■吳小姐話突然有隻野豬媽媽帶住一隻野豬仔喺山邊行出嚟搵食。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大豬唔理人　豬仔驚青<br />\n<br />\n下晝4點幾，佢哋行到紅梅谷自然教育徑，就快落到大圍，當佢哋沿石屎梯級行落去燒烤場嗰陣，喺吳小姐前面3至4級位置，突然有隻野豬媽媽帶住一隻野豬仔喺山邊行出嚟搵食，吳小姐話初時都有啲驚，見野豬好似唔係好理人，佢又唔敢再行近，於是停低影相，過咗大約5分鐘，野豬聽到人講嘢聲先慌失失咁跑番入叢林。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋繼續落山，接近燒烤場又見到一群6、7隻野豬仔，細隻嘅比較驚青，一聽到有聲就跑走。吳小姐話聽其他行山人士講，估計有人喺度餵野豬，所以越嚟越多野豬走嚟等食。吳小姐都係第一次見到咁大班野豬喺面前行過，佢認為人類同野生動物可以和平共處，不過佢就唔贊成餵野豬嘞，驚會好似馬騮咁唔驚人，見到人拎住膠袋就搶嘢食。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：為孫仔滿月買禮盒　嫲嫲漏低利是金　返轉頭冇咗<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：賣月餅券　惠康一開門即斷貨"},{"pid":"a95625011713e72fa708f0f7005261ee279d7a4b","tid":761374,"uid":148652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:54:35.000Z","msg":"真心想睇幾時有野豬攻擊個班餵野豬既人，on9先會餵野豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93f03e9d71df74a720d15b53954d96aed05ed59","tid":761374,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"野豬危險過馬嬲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fed681d5309adcc1d1b1d65e19bb96c842c5a29","tid":761374,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"捉左細既做燒乳豬"},{"pid":"24591d1011f418bd74a3fca96e06fa32c283b41d","tid":761374,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a93f03e9d71df74a720d15b53954d96aed05ed59","tid":761374,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"野豬危險過馬嬲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"論攻擊性馬嬲係大好多"}]}